revision.text: ==English== ===Etymology=== Probably related to {{m|en|yampah}}, from {{uder|en|shh|-}}. ===Noun=== {{en-noun|-}} # An [[umbelliferous]] [[plant]], {{taxlink|Perideridia gairdneri|species|noshow=1}}, native to [[California]], whose tubers were used as food by Native Americans. ===See also=== * {{l|en|yampah}} [[Category:en:Celery family plants]] [[Category:en:Root vegetables]]
